Package fr.upmc.datacenter.hardware.computers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Computer
    The class Computer implements a component that represents a computer in a data center.
    Computer.AllocatedCore
    The class AllocatedCore implements object collecting information about cores allocated to an Application VM.
    ComputerDynamicState
    The class ComputerDynamicState implements objects representing a snapshot of the dynamic state of a computer component to be pulled or pushed through the dynamic state data interface.
    ComputerStaticState
    The class ComputerStaticState implements objects representing a snapshot of the static state of a computer component to be pulled or pushed through the static state data interface.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Computer.ComputerPortTypes
    The three types of interfaces offered by Computer.
